data.description: Come check out this meticulously maintained brick beauty! Upon entry, you'll be captivated by the elegant details and impeccable craftsmanship found throughout. The spacious kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting beautiful wooden cabinetry, ample counter space, and a convenient island that is perfect for meal prep and entertaining. Natural light floods the kitchen and living area, thanks to the skylight and large windows, creating a bright and cheerful ambiance. The living area offers generous space, making it ideal for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying cozy evenings by the fireplace. With three bedrooms the possibilities for this home are endless. Outside the covered patio area provides endless options for gardening, entertaining, or simply relaxing on those warm summer evenings. Start your summer here - give us a call today!
